QEMU Emulation of RISC-V Virtual Machine
----------------------------------------

The QEMU emulator has machine support for the RISCV/qemu virtual board.


BOOTING
-------

To run the generated images do:

    qemu-system-riscv64 \
	-nographic \
	-machine virt \
	-bios images/fw_jump.elf \
	-kernel images/Image \
	-drive file=images/rootfs.bin,format=raw,id=hd0 \
	-device virtio-blk-device,drive=hd0 \
	-append "console=ttyS0 root=/dev/vda"

The serial console output will come out on the same device that you
run this on.

